The Hammersmith & Fulham Council website requires a more recent version of your web browser.

Newer browsers protect you better against scams, viruses, trojans, phishing and other threats. They also fix security holes in your current browser!

Updating your browser is easy and free

Find the latest version for your browser below.

  • Internet Explorer
  • Google Chrome
  • Firefox
  • Safari
  • Browser-Update.org – update your browser

If you are already using IE9 or above and are still seeing this message, it may be that your browser is set to view this website in compatability view mode. In IE11 you can check whether compatibility mode is activated for lbhf.gov.uk by clicking the gears icon and clicking Compatibility View settings. If lbhf.gov.uk appears in the list of sites, please remove it and retry.

Find out more about IE and compatability mode settings from Microsoft.
